Lazerbeak12345:
It should work using this code (found on http://hassankhan.me/emojify.js/):

```
emojify.setConfig({
   emojify_tag_type : 'div',           // Only run emojify.js on this element
    only_crawl_id    : null,            // Use to restrict where emojify.js applies
    img_dir          : 'images/emoji',  // Directory for emoji images
    ignored_tags     : {                // Ignore the following tags
        'SCRIPT'  : 1,
        'TEXTAREA': 1,
        'A'       : 1,
        'PRE'     : 1,
        'CODE'    : 1
    }
});
emojify.run();
```
. I noticed that if I get the 1.1.0 from the cdnjs link in the README.md file it works just fine.
. Another idea `:1:` = `:one:` = :one: (for each number 0-10)
. perhaps even something with :}
